      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Hi there! It's understandable to be uneasy about these persistent dreams, but it's highly unlikely that your subconscious is directly influenced by advertisements during sleep. Sometimes our sleep patterns can cause us to dream of things we've seen recently or are stressed about. If these dreams are really bothering you, maybe consult a healthcare professional for peace of mind. Rest assured, it's just your imagination and nothing sinister!",
